caption: This place must be for pastrami.  They handed me directions to King Gyro, as soon I asked for lamb from a skewer.
Very friendly over the phone, really quick delivery, and REALLY AMAZING FOOD!!! Thank You!!!

I've been grabbing lunch here for the past couple of days! Their food is really good and well worth the money. You really get a lot of bang for your buck here. Plus they are prompt and quick. I highly recommend their sandwiches, and CORN FRITTERS. Please do yourself a favor and get an order of corn fritters! So sweet and crunchy. Never stop making these. They are my go to lunch spot.
